onRenterChanged(address).details: Only callable by the rental auction contract.

startAuction().details: Only callable by the owner. If the ERC721 token is not owned by this contract, it will be pulled in (or the transaction will revert). Calls the unpause function on the rental auction contract.

stopAuction().details: Only callable by the owner. Calls the pause function on the rental auction contract.

returns._0: The address of the ERC721 token contract

withdrawToken().details: Only callable by the owner. Reverts if the auction is not paused.

onRenterChanged(address).notice: Called by the rental auction contract when the renter has changed

owner().notice: The owner of this controller contract

rentalAuction().notice: The rental auction contract that this controller is attached to

transferOwnership(address).notice: Transfers ownership of this controller contract to a new owner.

withdrawToken().notice: Withdraws the ERC721 token from this contract to the contract owner.
